\n
I am a Ph.D. student in [https://www.cs.umn.edu/ Computer Science & Engineering] at [https://twin-cities.umn.edu/ University of Minnesota, Twin Cities]. I am fortunate to be advised by Prof. [https://cse.umn.edu/ece/vladimir-cherkassky Vladimir Cherkassky] and Prof. [https://sunju.org/ Ju Sun]. Simultaneously, I am pursuing the minor degree (doctoral) in [https://healthinformatics.umn.edu/ Health Informatics]. Before starting my Ph.D. study, I have obtained my Master and Bachelor degree in Computer Science at [https://ccst.jlu.edu.cn/ Jilin University] where I was advised by Prof. [http://ccst.jlu.edu.cn/info/1026/15227.htm Liang Hu].




I am interested in /machine learning/, /deep learning/, /computer vision/, /image processing/, and /the general applications of machine learning\/deep learning in healthcare and medical settings/.







= News
. [2021-12:] Our paper /Early Stopping for Deep Image Prior/ is available at [https://arxiv.org/abs/2112.06074 arXiv].\n
. [2021-10:] Our paper /Self-Validation: Early Stopping for Single-Instance Deep Generative Priors/ has been accepted by [https://arxiv.org/abs/2110.12271 BMVC2021].\n
. [2021-06:] The preprint of our study about transfer learning in medical imaging is available at [https://arxiv.org/abs/2106.05152 arXiv].\n
. [2021-06:] The preprint of our study on COVID-19 is available at [https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2021.06.04.21258316v1 medRxiv].\n
. [2021-04:] Our paper with [https://med.umn.edu/ Medical School] has been accepted by [https://academic.oup.com/neurosurgery Neurosurgery].\n
. [2020-09:] Press coverage about our COVID-19 healthcare project is available at [https://cse.umn.edu/college/feature-stories/artificial-intelligence-real-life-results CSE News], [https://twin-cities.umn.edu/news-events/university-minnesota-develops-ai-algorithm-analyze-chest-x-rays-covid-19 UMN News], and [https://www.startribune.com/m-health-fairview-x-ray-analysis-helps-find-covid/572605252/ StarTribune].


